name: Cow Duty (Deber de Vaca)
description:
Warning, warning, warning, warning, warning, warning, warning, warning!

This is not a game, this is a evidence of  the thruth reality.

Hello human, you are about to unveil the typical conspiracy myth, to witness it with your own eyes and with it, to be able to say that this is true. Enjoy it or accept the consequences.

Influenced by the art of Rene Magritte paints(steel balls)and Earthworm Jim's cow loading screen.

Just tap across the screen and immerse yourself in the truth.

Made with Flickgame, 2021.
